Raytracer project for the Bachelor Thesis

Some cool introduction text.

############################################################

                         Usage

raytracer [options]

Allowed options:
  -h [ --help ]              produce help message
  --no_opengl                Do not use OpenGL
  -i [ --input-file ] arg    Input file
  -o [ --output-file ] arg   Output file
  -s [ --settings-file ] arg Settings file
  

############################################################

                     Settings-file
Each row in the settings file specifies the value for one
option. Option name is separated by a colon:

    option_name : value

Available options are:

width:int
height:int
opengl_version:int
use_first_bounce:bool

